sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant User
  participant Browser as Browser (React UI)
  participant Proxy as Vite Proxy
  participant API as FastAPI
  participant PG as PostgreSQL
  participant Redis as Redis

  User->>Browser: Open / (Dashboard)
  Browser->>Proxy: GET /api/v1/audit/stats?range=24h
  Proxy->>API: Forward request
  API->>PG: Query aggregated audit stats
  API-->>Proxy: Stats JSON
  Proxy-->>Browser: Stats JSON

  Browser->>Proxy: GET /api/v1/audit/records?limit=10&decision=block
  Proxy->>API: Forward request
  API->>PG: Query latest audit rows
  API-->>Proxy: Records JSON
  Proxy-->>Browser: Records JSON
  Browser-->>User: Render KPI cards + charts + table

  User->>Browser: Change namespace/time-range filter
  Browser->>Proxy: Re-fetch /api/v1/* with new query params
  Proxy->>API: Forward filtered requests
  API->>PG: Recompute filtered datasets
  API->>Redis: Read/write trust cache where needed
  API-->>Proxy: Filtered payloads
  Proxy-->>Browser: Updated data
  Browser-->>User: Re-render filtered dashboard/audit views

  User->>Browser: Open Policy Catalog and click Apply
  Browser->>Proxy: POST /api/v1/policies/{ns}/{class}/apply
  Proxy->>API: Forward mutation
  API->>PG: Persist policy/enforcement changes
  API-->>Proxy: Apply result
  Proxy-->>Browser: Apply result JSON
  Browser-->>User: Show updated policy state
